# Streamlit secrets template for suno-prompt-generator-pro.
#
# To enable Google Analytics 4 visitor counter:
#   1. Create a GA4 property at https://analytics.google.com
#      (Web stream, URL: https://ironvespers.streamlit.app/)
#   2. Copy the Measurement ID (looks like G-XXXXXXXXXX)
#   3. For LOCAL dev: paste it into a file at .streamlit/secrets.toml
#        echo 'GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID = "G-XXXXXXXXXX"' > .streamlit/secrets.toml
#      (NEVER commit this file — it's in .gitignore)
#   4. For STREAMLIT CLOUD: paste it into the app's Secrets field:
#        https://share.streamlit.io/  ->  [your app]  ->  Settings  ->  Secrets
#        Format:
#          GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID = "G-XXXXXXXXXX"
#
# The app's GA4 injection is at suno_prompt_generator_pro.py around line 1340.
# If GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID is unset (e.g. during local dev), the snippet is skipped
# silently — no errors, no UI changes.

# === Default Measurement ID for HavokRabbit / Suno-prompts-pro ===
# This ID is safe to commit publicly — measurement IDs are only "claimed"
# by the GA4 property owner. Clone this repo and swap to your own.
GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID = "G-FPS8T1J4K0"
